Package: discretes
Type: Package
Title: Countable Numeric Sets
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Vincenzo", "Coia",
      email = "vincenzo.coia@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    )
  )
Description: While it is impossible to create an infinite-length numeric
    vector such as the set of all integers, this package provides a work-around
    by allowing you to create countable sets and manipulate them. Probe the
    set by walking forwards or backwards, retrieving limit points ('sinks'),
    checking membership, and more.
